title: Directs the division of veterans' affairs to establish and distribute a veterans' bill of rights, and to contract with veterans' services outreach programs
summary: Directs the division of veterans' affairs to establish and distribute a veterans' bill of rights, and to contract with veterans' services outreach programs.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the executive law, in relation to establishing a "veterans' bill of rights" directing the division of veterans' affairs to provide for the establishment and certification of veterans' services outreach programs
